.SH NAME
udpdump \- Provide an UDP receiver that gets packets from network devices (like Aruba routers) and exports them in PCAP format.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
\&\fBudpdump\fR
[\ \fB\-\-help\fR\ ]
